ActNational Round Table on the Environment and the Economy Act
PrecisAppointment of RICHARD DROUIN, Q.C., of Sillery, Quebec, and DAVID KERR of Toronto, Ontario, to be members of the National Round Table on the Environment and the Economy, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective April 9, 2005.
